    <section class="my-4" data-aos="fade-right">
      <h2 class="my-4 text-2xl">Interests</h2>
      <p>
        As a software engineer, my passions extend beyond the digital realm into the tangible world
        of electronics, mechanical work, camping, and hiking. In programming, I find the creative
        challenge of problem-solving exhilarating, constantly seeking elegant solutions to complex
